video.title: Terrace House: Boys & Girls in the City
video.synopsis: A new set of six men and women start their lives together under one roof. All they get is a fabulous home and a car. As always, there is no script.

episodes.synopsis: One summer's day, six young strangers move into a house together and start living an unscripted drama.
episodes.title: New Boys, New Girls, New City

episodes.synopsis: Everyone changes into swimsuits after lunch and heads to the pool on the terrace. The boys are excited at the sight of the girls in their swimsuits.
episodes.title: Three Crushes

episodes.synopsis: The roommates celebrate tap dancer Yuuki's birthday. However, his harsh words trigger tears from both Mizuki and Yuriko.
episodes.title: Dream Police

episodes.synopsis: Makoto and Minori go out to dinner alone together. Yuuki asks Yuriko out on a date, but she's had a bit too much sake to drink. What will she say?
episodes.title: In Tears Again

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya rocks the house by declaring he'll take each of the three girls on a date this summer. Meanwhile, something is up with Minori and Makoto.
episodes.title: Eenie Meenie Miney Mo

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya declared he would go on a date with all three of the girls. First comes Mizuki, and next is Yuriko, but her date opens a whole can of worms.
episodes.title: All Screwed Up

episodes.synopsis: Makoto angers Tatsuya with his rash behavior but shows no signs of remorse, creating a touch-and-go situation in the boys' room.
episodes.title: Showing His True Colors

episodes.synopsis: Minori loses interest as she sees how Makoto behaves. Tatsuya reflects on his dates with the three girls in an effort to choose one as his lover.
episodes.title: Late Night Poolside

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya and Minori go on a second date. Tatsuya tells her how he feels but says she need not give her answer now. Makoto has a present for Minori.
episodes.title: What a Good Day!

episodes.synopsis: Unable to forget her ex, Yuriko calls and asks to see him. Meanwhile, after receiving a present from Makoto, Minori talks to him about her feelings.
episodes.title: Before He Says the Words...

episodes.synopsis: At the Girls Award event, Tatsuya and Minori meet former member Seina, who encourages their budding relationship. A new member arrives from overseas.
episodes.title: Boy from the Rainbow State

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya finally asks Minori to officially be his girlfriend. How will she answer? Hawaii-born Arman, the newest housemate, asks Mizuki out on a date.
episodes.title: Is She Just Best of Three?

episodes.synopsis: Yuriko confesses her feelings to her ex before leaving the house. And her ex's reply? The boys get excited over the arrival of the new girl member.
episodes.title: Who Will Survive?

episodes.synopsis: Arisa's arrival to the house excites Arman and Yuuki because she's "their type." Meanwhile, Tatsuya and Minori find it hard to take the next step.
episodes.title: Ikujinashi

episodes.synopsis: A kiss takes Tatsuya and Minori's relationship to the next level. Arisa and Arman head to Mt. Takao on a date. But Mizuki also has feelings for Arman.
episodes.title: Heating Up for Someone Else

episodes.synopsis: Arisa grows closer to Arman after having gone out on a number of dates. Yuuki, who also hopes to ask Arisa out, tries hard to steal her attention.
episodes.title: Magic Spell "Costco"

episodes.synopsis: Arman et al. prepare the Japanese-style room for Minori and Tatsuya, now a couple. Arisa promises she will go anywhere with Arman if he wins his game.
episodes.title: Anywhere for You

episodes.synopsis: Minori confesses her relationship issues with Tatsuya to her older sister, Kurumi, who asks Minori whether the two are having make-up sex or not.
episodes.title: Worst Date Ever

episodes.synopsis: Arman and Arisa go out on a Christmas dinner date. The two hold hands and enjoy the Christmas lights. Then, Arman expresses his feelings to Arisa.
episodes.title: A Christmas Nightmare

episodes.synopsis: Excitement buzzes as Terrace House welcomes two new members. But upon Natsumi's arrival, an incident causes a clash between her and Minori.
episodes.title: Scissorhands

episodes.synopsis: New member Natsumi invites Arman out to the beach one morning. Later that day, Arman fixes the busy Arisa a Hawaiian fish salad called "poke."
episodes.title: Case of Poke Bowl

episodes.synopsis: One night, the housemates discover they have run out of food. Minori suggests eating the fancy wagyu beef that Tatsuya got as a present at work.
episodes.title: Case of the Meat

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya is furious with his housemates for eating his beef without his permission. Minori's older sister comes to visit and reasons with him.
episodes.title: No Use Crying Over Meat

episodes.synopsis: Tatsuya and Minori depart from the house as a couple after seven months. Upon arrival, the new girl becomes an instant love interest among the boys.
episodes.title: New It Girl in the City

episodes.synopsis: Aspiring architect Yuto Handa moves in after Misaki. He intends to complete his studies at Harvard and attracts the attention of the female residents.
episodes.title: Mr. Perfect in the City

episodes.synopsis: Hikaru is interested in the new housemate Misaki. When she talks about her ex, he doesn't hide his irritation. The next day, when the two are alone...
episodes.title: Love Is in the Air

episodes.synopsis: Hikaru takes Misaki for a romantic motorbike ride to the beach. Later, Misaki tells Natsumi that she wishes the date had lasted forever.
episodes.title: Always Smiling With You

episodes.synopsis: Yuto promises to go fishing with Natsumi, but he changes his mind and tells her he cant go because of his girlfriend. Natsumi starts to cry.
episodes.title: Cry, Cry, Cry

episodes.synopsis: High school student Riko Nagai, who recently won a national beauty contest, joins the gang. Misaki quickly befriends her and they chat about Hikaru.
episodes.title: Nightie Nightmare

episodes.synopsis: When Misaki buys some sleepwear with Hikaru's opinion in mind, Natsumi comments on it and the two get into an argument. Yuto sides against Natsumi.
episodes.title: Girl's Decision in Love

episodes.synopsis: Misaki confesses her feelings to Hikaru. That night, she says something that makes Natsumi incredibly angry and winds up paying the price for it.
episodes.title: Natsumi & Fuyumi

episodes.synopsis: When Hikaru suddenly declares that he will leave the house with Natsumi, the rest of the members are shocked. Misaki has a talk with him in private.
episodes.title: Shall We "Pas de Deux"?

episodes.synopsis: Hayato promises to go on a date with Riko, but she worries she's too young for him. During the welcome party, an unexpected surprise occurs.
episodes.title: First Dip in the Pool

episodes.synopsis: Riko asks Hayato if he thinks she's immature, but he reassures her. They decide on Tsukiji for their second date. Arman participates in a festival.
episodes.title: Hamburg x Hamburg

episodes.synopsis: Momoka works up the courage to ask Arman out to the beach. Hayato and Riko enjoy their date at Tsukiji. Meanwhile, Yuto makes a decision.
episodes.title: Bye Bye Mr. Perfect

episodes.synopsis: Shortly after Handa's departure, Yuuki arrives at the house. Good looking and tall, he's just Riko's type. But he has his eyes on someone else.
episodes.title: Byrnes Sandwich

episodes.synopsis: Yuuki's had his eye on Misaki ever since moving in and asks her out on a date. Misaki tells him about her unrequited feelings for Hikaru.
episodes.title: Slow Down Your Love

episodes.synopsis: After their date ends awkwardly, Riko tries to clear the air with Hayato. Meanwhile, Momoka faces a life-changing contest.
episodes.title: Quick to Say I Love You

episodes.synopsis: During Misaki's birthday party, Yuuki can't control himself and confesses his feelings for Misaki. The next morning, she asks if he remembers.
episodes.title: Rocket Girl Dives Into Love

episodes.synopsis: Recent entrant Masako quickly declares her fondness for Hayato and promises to cook with him. One night, the two of them spend time alone at the pool.
episodes.title: Midsummer Intimacy

episodes.synopsis: Yuuki goes on his first drive with Misaki to Yokohama, where she once fell out of love. He finally tells her how he really feels about her.
episodes.title: Better Luck This Time

episodes.synopsis: Masako feels even more strongly about Hayato and, after seeing him with Riko, asks him out on a date. Arman goes out for nighttime skateboarding.
episodes.title: Fragile Boy, Fragile Girl

episodes.synopsis: Riko and Hayato's date to see the fireworks ends uneventfully. He says that he doesn't see her as a woman, but this statement proves consequential.
episodes.title: Kiss and Tell

episodes.synopsis: Despite the apparent lack of progress in Riko and Hayato's relationship, the other housemates question them upon learning they have already kissed.
episodes.title: Price of a Lie

episodes.synopsis: The house members confront Hayato and Riko about the lies they told about their relationship. Hayato remains silent and all eyes turn to Riko.
episodes.title: The Riko Special

episodes.synopsis: In the season finale, as the evening of their arrangement arrives, Hayato prepares for Riko in his restaurant. But she may be headed somewhere else.
episodes.title: Bye Bye Terrace House in the City
